    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin adds a \u201cTabs\u201d section to the admin panel which allows you to create tabbed content for your website the easy way. You can quickly add your content to your different tabs, choose a color, re-order them at anytime and display them anywhere with a simple shortcode. What you see is what you get, and it\u2019s totally free.<\/p>\n<p>&#091;Compatible with PHP 8.&#093;<\/p>\n<h4>No limitation for the Free version<\/h4>\n<p>The free version of the Responsive Tabs plugin is <strong>not limited<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/items\/responsive-tabs-pro\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PRO version<\/a> adds new features such as new styling settings and <strong>icons<\/strong> (from font-awesome).<\/p>\n<h4>Fully translatable<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>POT files included (\/lang\/)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Available fields<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Title<\/li>\n<li>Content (text\/images\/anything)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Available settings<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Breakpoint (decide when the tabs should shrink into an accordion)<\/li>\n<li>Color<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Usage<\/h4>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-responsive-tabs-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> if you need more information on how to use this plugin.<\/p>\n<h4>Support<\/h4>\n<p>Find help in <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">our support plaftorm<\/a> for this plugin (we\u2019ll answer you fast, promise).<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>Installation<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>In your WordPress admin panel, go to Plugins &gt; New Plugin<\/li>\n<li>Find our Responsive Tabs plugin by WP Darko and click Install now<\/li>\n<li>Alternatively, download the plugin and upload the contents of responsive-tabs.zip to your plugins directory, which usually is \/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin<\/li>\n<li>Enjoy<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Usage<\/h4>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-responsive-tabs-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> for information on how to use it.<\/p>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='no%20limitation%20for%20the%20free%20version'>\nNo limitation for the Free version\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>The free version of the Responsive Tabs plugin is <strong>not limited<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/items\/responsive-tabs-pro\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PRO version<\/a> adds new features such as new styling settings and <strong>icons<\/strong> (from font-awesome).<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='fully%20translatable'>\nFully translatable\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li>POT files included (\/lang\/)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='usage'>\nUsage\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-responsive-tabs-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> if you need more information on how to use this plugin.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='support'>\nSupport\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Find help on <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">our support plaftorm<\/a> for this plugin (we\u2019ll answer you fast, promise).<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>4.0.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed vulnerability issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed vulnerability issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed conflict with ACF &amp; TinyMCE<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated deprecated jQuery code<\/li>\n<li>Fixed Instant Preview issue<\/li>\n<li>Fixed color pickers bug<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed metabox handles styles<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed minor CSS issue.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed deprecated code.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>4.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds a new admin interface (faster and more intuitive).<\/li>\n<li>Adds tab labels background setting.<\/li>\n<li>Adds Instant preview to see what the tab sets look like without refreshing the page or publishing a post.<\/li>\n<li>Fixes various PHP errors.<\/li>\n<li>Fixes repeatable WordPress text editor.<\/li>\n<li>Fixes checkbox issues when adding more tabs to a tab set.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.3.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Add Media button issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add TinyMCE for content field<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix tab removal issue (working on better solution)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated read file<\/li>\n<li>Add metabox framework as dependency<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix minor CSS bugs<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Allow iframe in tab content<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugin is now translation ready<\/li>\n<li>Add French translation<\/li>\n<li>Add Spanish translation<\/li>\n<li>Fix auto-scrolling on tab click<\/li>\n<li>Fix various PHP errors<\/li>\n<li>Fix major CSS bug (tab spacing)<\/li>\n<li>Cleaner edit screen<\/li>\n<li>Security update<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix the update process<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New admin interface (new framework)<\/li>\n<li>Allow forcing plugin&#8217;s original fonts<\/li>\n<li>Add docs and support forums links<\/li>\n<li>Add instructions<\/li>\n<li>Cleaning code<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Major styling bug fixes (spacing, fonts)<\/li>\n<li>Better adapts to your theme<\/li>\n<li>Bigger content field when editing your tabs (UX)<\/li>\n<li>Fix 1 PHP errors<\/li>\n<li>Cleaning code<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a unique class to tab\u2019s links for customization (user request)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add nested shortcode support<\/li>\n<li>Styling bug fixes for many themes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor bug fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix background problem when add images to the tabs<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor bug fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor bug fixes<\/li>\n<li>Prevent conflicts between plugins<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor CSS bug fixes<\/li>\n<li>Prevent conflicts between plugins<\/li>\n<li>Automatic recovery of all tabs when switching to PRO version<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release (yay!)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1026652\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1026652\" alt=\"Displaying the tabs (front view)\"><\/a><p>Displaying the tabs (front view)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1026652\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1026652\" alt=\"Displaying the tabs 2 (front view)\"><\/a><p>Displaying the tabs 2 (front view)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=1948506\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=1948506\" alt=\"Creating tabs (admin view)\"><\/a><p>Creating tabs (admin view)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=1020638\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-tabs\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=1020638\" alt=\"Finding the shortcode (admin view)\"><\/a><p>Finding the shortcode (admin view)<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Don\u2019t give them your credit card number<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/connorblandford\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5492b62be070a1ca4304ae1372253565?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5492b62be070a1ca4304ae1372253565?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/connorblandford\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">connorblandford<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 9, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The tabs admittedly work pretty nicely if you are just figuring things out.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\"><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I\u2019ve been trying to cancel this service for 3 years though and they keep charging me.  Don\u2019t give them your card details.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice plugin but not secure<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dustin1701\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1d4aef3499100e47a3b2adf9461c1d71?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1d4aef3499100e47a3b2adf9461c1d71?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dustin1701\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dustin M\u00fcller <small>(dustin1701)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 7, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">The Plugin have vulnerabilities, because it use unsecure XSS.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Support<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mbajadek\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fe5d84c334c42a93cd3b1aeaf0c9af15?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fe5d84c334c42a93cd3b1aeaf0c9af15?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mbajadek\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mbajadek<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 22, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Their support is A+ .. they responded to my issue in a very timely fashion.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice &amp; lightweight<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hj\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/35860d0f015147621d706585db522b0e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/35860d0f015147621d706585db522b0e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hj\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hj<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 24, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Nice and lightweight plugin, pretty easy to follow and use right out of the box - created just what I wanted.  Not many bells and whistles in the free version, a bit more dressing in the Pro version.\nHowever, I've had a repeated problem of content not showing in the edit box when I want to edit a tab's content.  The content is definitely there, it shows in the tab mini-view area and on the live site - but hit the edit button and I've frequently, though not all the time, got an edit window with no visible content.\nCould be a bug? Could be the browser? (Firefox 94 on Mac OSX).\nI like it for its much smaller footprint than other plugins. But that content edit issue needs fixing.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">love the fast support<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/beardev\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/38b303424367f7605dc66034008f2615?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/38b303424367f7605dc66034008f2615?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/beardev\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">beardev<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 26, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">fast answer, fast decision, that's what we like about that developer!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Limited version<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/balashinde\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b46837b3df22f4b68d35b2124d228091?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b46837b3df22f4b68d35b2124d228091?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/balashinde\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">balashinde<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 22, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">The free version of the Responsive Tabs plugin is limited. You can't change Tab's color.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic Plugin - did the job<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nixtainternet\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d97aaf54cb635fece707ddb9dbd7fdd5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d97aaf54cb635fece707ddb9dbd7fdd5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nixtainternet\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nixtainternet<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 9, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Modern, responsive plugin that made my tabs a breeze !! Highly recommended!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Outstanding plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dabooker\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/54ac068f36903271da6d200bb5751bae?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/54ac068f36903271da6d200bb5751bae?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dabooker\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dennis Booker <small>(dabooker)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 28, 2018<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I've been using both the free and pro version of Responsive Tabs for over a year and recommend it highly.  The UI is pretty easy to navigate and the most recent update is very nice.  Support questions are answered quickly and unlike some they will help if you want to make custom css changes.  Nice plugin and nice folks.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Need tab builder inside page\/post<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/weblink\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/24130735f3dd2610ceda4fabfd92c0ff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/24130735f3dd2610ceda4fabfd92c0ff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/weblink\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">weblink<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 12, 2018<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">The fact that you have to build your tabbed pages outside the the page\/post system is a deal breaker for me. Sorry it didn't work out. Was initially excited to see your plugin. <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very responsive<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/artbiz\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8fbe46f36067f6975f787b607b31d3ae?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/8fbe46f36067f6975f787b607b31d3ae?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/artbiz\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">artbiz<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 6, 2018<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">The plugin developer was very quick to help the not for profit site were I installed the plugin. \n\nThanks man!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
